#: src/actions/catalog.rs:32 src/actions/runtime.rs:46
#: src/ui/window/groups.rs:164
msgid "Instalar suporte principal"
msgstr "Install core support"

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:34
msgid ""
"Instala Galaxy Book Câmera, driver OV02C10 e suporte MAX98390 para começar "
"pelo setup sem depender de instalação manual dos outros pacotes."
msgstr ""
"Installs Galaxy Book Camera, the OV02C10 driver and MAX98390 support so "
"setup can start without depending on manual installation of the other "
"packages."

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:38 src/actions/runtime.rs:60
#: src/ui/window/groups.rs:165
msgid "Instalar suporte da câmera"
msgstr "Install camera support"

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:40
msgid ""
"Instala o driver corrigido e o aplicativo Galaxy Book Câmera usando "
"privilégios administrativos."
msgstr ""
"Installs the patched driver and the Galaxy Book Camera app using "
"administrative privileges."

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:44 src/actions/runtime.rs:74
#: src/ui/window/groups.rs:166
msgid "Reparar o driver"
msgstr "Repair driver"

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:46
msgid ""
"Reconstrói o módulo com akmods para o kernel atual e atualiza a árvore de "
"módulos."
msgstr ""
"Rebuilds the module with akmods for the current kernel and updates the "
"module tree."

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:50 src/actions/runtime.rs:88
#: src/ui/window/groups.rs:168
msgid "Habilitar driver da câmera"
msgstr "Enable camera driver"

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:52
msgid ""
"Garante o carregamento do ov02c10 no boot, ajusta o softdep do IPU6 e "
"carrega o módulo agora no kernel."
msgstr ""
"Ensures ov02c10 loads at boot, adjusts the IPU6 softdep and loads the module "
"into the kernel now."

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:56 src/actions/runtime.rs:102
#: src/ui/window/groups.rs:170
msgid "Ajustar prioridade do driver"
msgstr "Prioritize driver"

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:58
msgid ""
"Compila o módulo corrigido, assina quando o Secure Boot estiver ativo e o "
"instala em /lib/modules/.../updates sem compressão incompatível."
msgstr ""
"Compiles the patched module, signs it when Secure Boot is enabled and "
"installs it in /lib/modules/.../updates without incompatible compression."

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:62 src/actions/runtime.rs:116
#: src/ui/window/groups.rs:172
msgid "Restaurar stack Intel IPU6"
msgstr "Restore Intel IPU6 stack"

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:64
msgid ""
"Remove o override manual em /updates, reinstala o stack Intel empacotado e "
"volta ao caminho que já funcionava com a câmera do sistema."
msgstr ""
"Removes the manual override in /updates, reinstalls the packaged Intel stack "
"and returns to the path that already worked with the system camera."

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:68 src/actions/runtime.rs:130
#: src/ui/window/groups.rs:174
msgid "Ativar câmera para navegador"
msgstr "Enable browser camera"

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:70
msgid ""
"Expõe a câmera interna como webcam V4L2 para Meet, Discord, Teams e outros "
"apps WebRTC usando o bridge do sistema e oculta os nós crus do IPU6 no "
"PipeWire."
msgstr ""
"Exposes the internal camera as a V4L2 webcam for Meet, Discord, Teams and "
"other WebRTC apps using the system bridge and hides the raw IPU6 nodes in "
"PipeWire."

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:74 src/actions/runtime.rs:144
#: src/ui/window/groups.rs:176
msgid "Ativar alto-falantes internos"
msgstr "Enable internal speakers"

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:76
msgid ""
"Instala o suporte MAX98390, reconstrói os módulos dos amplificadores, "
"instala manualmente o driver no kernel atual quando necessário e habilita o "
"serviço de I2C usado pelos alto-falantes internos."
msgstr ""
"Installs MAX98390 support, rebuilds the amplifier modules, manually installs "
"the driver into the current kernel when needed and enables the I2C service "
"used by the internal speakers."

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:80 src/actions/runtime.rs:158
#: src/ui/window/groups.rs:177
msgid "Reparar suporte NVIDIA"
msgstr "Repair NVIDIA support"

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:82
msgid ""
"Instala ou reconstrói o akmod-nvidia para o kernel atual. O nvidia-smi "
"permanece opcional."
msgstr ""
"Installs or rebuilds akmod-nvidia for the current kernel. nvidia-smi remains "
"optional."

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:86 src/actions/runtime.rs:172
#: src/ui/window/groups.rs:178
msgid "Definir perfil balanceado"
msgstr "Set balanced profile"

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:88
msgid ""
"Aplica o perfil balanced da plataforma para uso geral, equilibrando "
"ventoinha, temperatura e desempenho."
msgstr ""
"Applies the platform balanced profile for general use, balancing fan noise, "
"temperature and performance."

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:92 src/actions/runtime.rs:186
#: src/ui/window/groups.rs:180
msgid "Ativar histórico da área de transferência"
msgstr "Enable clipboard history"

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:94
msgid ""
"Instala e habilita a extensão de clipboard usada como perfil recomendado "
"neste notebook."
msgstr ""
"Installs and enables the clipboard extension used as the recommended profile "
"on this notebook."

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:98 src/actions/runtime.rs:200
#: src/ui/window/groups.rs:181
msgid "Ativar GSConnect"
msgstr "Enable GSConnect"

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:100
msgid ""
"Instala o GSConnect, habilita a extensão e reaplica o perfil usado neste "
"notebook para integração com o celular."
msgstr ""
"Installs GSConnect, enables the extension and reapplies the profile used on "
"this notebook for phone integration."

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:104 src/actions/runtime.rs:216
#: src/ui/window/groups.rs:183
msgid "Ativar ícones na área de trabalho"
msgstr "Enable desktop icons"

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:106
msgid ""
"Instala o Desktop Icons NG, habilita a extensão e reaplica o perfil usado "
"neste notebook."
msgstr ""
"Installs Desktop Icons NG, enables the extension and reapplies the profile "
"used on this notebook."

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:110 src/actions/runtime.rs:230
#: src/ui/window/groups.rs:184
msgid "Aplicar perfil da dock"
msgstr "Apply dock profile"

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:112
msgid ""
"Ativa o Dash to Dock e reaplica a dock inferior auto-ocultável, com clique "
"ciclando janelas, prévia, lixeira e unidades montadas visíveis."
msgstr ""
"Enables Dash to Dock and reapplies the auto-hiding bottom dock, with click-"
"to-cycle windows, previews, trash and mounted drives visible."

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:116 src/actions/runtime.rs:238
#: src/ui/window/groups.rs:185
msgid "Reiniciar o sistema"
msgstr "Reboot system"

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:118
msgid ""
"Aplica mudanças pendentes do driver e reinicia a sessão inteira do notebook."
msgstr ""
"Applies pending driver changes and reboots the notebook's entire session."

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:122 src/ui/window/groups.rs:186
msgid "Abrir Galaxy Book Câmera"
msgstr "Open Galaxy Book Camera"

#: src/actions/catalog.rs:124
msgid ""
"Abre o aplicativo final da câmera quando ele estiver instalado no sistema."
msgstr "Opens the final camera app when it is installed on the system."

#: src/actions/runtime.rs:48
msgid ""
"Pacotes principais instalados. Atualize o diagnóstico e use as ações "
"específicas se câmera ou alto-falantes ainda precisarem de ajuste."
msgstr ""
"Core packages installed. Refresh diagnostics and use the specific actions if "
"camera or speakers still need adjustment."

#: src/actions/runtime.rs:62
msgid "Instalação concluída. Reinicie o sistema para carregar o driver."
msgstr "Installation completed. Reboot the system to load the driver."

#: src/actions/runtime.rs:76
msgid "Reparo concluído. Reinicie o sistema para aplicar o módulo atualizado."
msgstr "Repair completed. Reboot the system to apply the updated module."

#: src/actions/runtime.rs:90
msgid ""
"Carregamento do ov02c10 ajustado. Se a câmera ainda não aparecer, reinicie o "
"sistema para validar o boot completo."
msgstr ""
"ov02c10 loading has been adjusted. If the camera still does not appear, "
"reboot the system to validate a full boot."

#: src/actions/runtime.rs:104
msgid ""
"Ajuste concluído. Se o módulo ainda estiver em uso, reinicie o sistema antes "
"de validar a câmera."
msgstr ""
"Adjustment completed. If the module is still in use, reboot the system "
"before validating the camera."

#: src/actions/runtime.rs:118
msgid ""
"Restauração concluída. Se a câmera continuar ausente no libcamera, reinicie "
"o sistema antes de validar novamente."
msgstr ""
"Restore completed. If the camera is still missing in libcamera, reboot the "
"system before validating again."

#: src/actions/runtime.rs:132
msgid ""
"Bridge V4L2 ativado. Se os nós crus do IPU6 ainda aparecerem na sessão "
"atual, faça logout/login antes de validar Meet, Discord e outros apps."
msgstr ""
"V4L2 bridge enabled. If the raw IPU6 nodes still appear in the current "
"session, log out and back in before validating Meet, Discord and other apps."

#: src/actions/runtime.rs:146
msgid ""
"Fluxo dos alto-falantes concluído. Se os módulos MAX98390 já aparecerem no "
"kernel, teste a saída Speaker imediatamente. Reinicie só se o sistema "
"continuar preso ao estado anterior."
msgstr ""
"Speaker flow completed. If the MAX98390 modules already appear in the "
"kernel, test the Speaker output immediately. Reboot only if the system "
"remains stuck in the previous state."

#: src/actions/runtime.rs:160
msgid ""
"Fluxo NVIDIA concluído. Reinicie o sistema se os módulos ainda não "
"aparecerem carregados."
msgstr ""
"NVIDIA flow completed. Reboot the system if the modules still do not appear "
"loaded."

#: src/actions/runtime.rs:174
msgid "Perfil balanced aplicado com sucesso."
msgstr "Balanced profile applied successfully."

#: src/actions/runtime.rs:188
msgid "Perfil do histórico da área de transferência aplicado com sucesso."
msgstr "Clipboard history profile applied successfully."

#: src/actions/runtime.rs:202
msgid "Perfil do GSConnect aplicado com sucesso."
msgstr "GSConnect profile applied successfully."

#: src/actions/runtime.rs:218
msgid "Perfil dos ícones da área de trabalho aplicado com sucesso."
msgstr "Desktop icons profile applied successfully."

#: src/actions/runtime.rs:232
msgid "Perfil da dock aplicado com sucesso."
msgstr "Dock profile applied successfully."

#: src/actions/runtime.rs:240
msgid "Reinicialização solicitada."
msgstr "Reboot requested."

#: src/actions/runtime.rs:250
#, rust-format
msgid "Falha ao abrir o app da câmera: {error}"
msgstr "Failed to open the camera app: {error}"

#: src/actions/runtime.rs:256
msgid "O Galaxy Book Câmera não foi encontrado no sistema."
msgstr "Galaxy Book Camera was not found on the system."

#: src/actions/runtime.rs:312
#, rust-format
msgid "Executando: {title}…"
msgstr "Running: {title}…"

#: src/actions/runtime.rs:372
msgid "Falha ao acompanhar a ação solicitada."
msgstr "Failed to track the requested action."

#: src/actions/runtime.rs:388
msgid "Saída da ação"
msgstr "Action output"

#: src/actions/runtime.rs:404
msgid "A ação falhou, mas não retornou saída textual."
msgstr "The action failed, but returned no textual output."

#: src/diagnostics/mod.rs:74
#, rust-format
msgid "{app_name}: {summary}"
msgstr "{app_name}: {summary}"

#: src/diagnostics/mod.rs:87
#, rust-format
